### MV INTERSECT
Returns a subset of the inputs sets that contains the intersection of values in provided mv arguments.

```esql
ROW a = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5], b = [2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
| EVAL finalValue = MV_INTERSECT(a, b)
| KEEP finalValue
```
